OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FThe decision was taken following the
OL,7,Fformer Tory deputy chairman's "refusal
OL,8,Fto apologise" for the remarks made on
OL,9,FFriday, a spokesperson for chief whip
OL,10,FSimon Hart said.
OL,12,FPressure had been mounting on Rishi
OL,13,FSunak to take action over the comments
OL,14,Ffrom the Ashfield MP, with Mr Khan
OL,15,Fsaying the "deafening silence" of the
OL,16,FPrime Minister and his Cabinet on the
OL,17,Fmatter amounted to condoning racism.
