OL,6,FA Conservative source was defending Mr
OL,7,FAnderson as recently as Friday evening
OL,8,Fbefore he was stripped of party
OL,9,Fsupport on Saturday afternoon.
OL,11,FCabinet minister Grant Shapps earlier
OL,12,Fdistanced himself from the remarks but
OL,13,Fstopped short of condemning his fellow
OL,14,FMP, arguing that people should be
OL,15,Fallowed to "speak their mind".
OL,17,FHowever, business minister Nus Ghani
OL,18,Fand senior backbencher Sir Sajid Javid
OL,19,Fwere among other Tory figures joining
OL,20,Fa growing chorus of criticism from
OL,21,Facross the political divide.
