OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FLabour called on Mr Sunak to "show
OL,7,Fsome leadership" and discipline the
OL,8,FMP, with shadow Cabinet Office
OL,9,Fminister Jonathan Ashworth writing a
OL,10,Fletter to the PM demanding the whip be
OL,11,Fwithdrawn.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Mr Hart said:
OL,14,F"Following his refusal to apologise
OL,15,Ffor comments made yesterday, the chief
OL,16,Fwhip has suspended the Conservative
OL,17,Fwhip from Lee Anderson MP."
