OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FReform UK leader Richard Tice
OL,7,Fpreviously suggested he has been in
OL,8,Ftouch with senior Conservative MPs who
OL,9,Fwere "absolutely furious" about the
OL,10,FGovernment's handling of immigration.
OL,12,FMr Anderson was deputy chairman of the
OL,13,FTory Party until resigning in January
OL,14,Fto rebel against Mr Sunak's
OL,15,Flegislation to revive the stalled plan
OL,16,Fto send some asylum seekers to Rwanda.
