OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FHe joined 58 other Conservatives to
OL,7,Fvote in favour of an amendment that
OL,8,Fsought to ensure UK and international
OL,9,Flaw cannot be used to prevent or delay
OL,10,Fa person being sent to Kigali under
OL,11,Fthe scheme.
OL,13,FMr Anderson has served since 2019 as
OL,14,FMP for Ashfield, one of the previously
OL,15,FLabour seats in the so-called red wall
OL,16,Fwhere voters switched to the Tories
OL,17,Fpost-Brexit to give Boris Johnson his
OL,18,Flandslide victory.
